snippet.title: Gates Of Integrity: Intro, character creation and first fights
snippet.description:
Gates Of Integrity is a humble tribute to the original Bard's Tale 1 and is available for free on itch:
https://tarjan.itch.io/gates-of-integrity

Music by Derek Fiechter:
https://derekfiechter.bandcamp.com/
